{"tid":2304803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「扯貓尾系列」教聯會就快成功爭取停課？","createTime":"2020-11-29T06:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T06:49:50.000Z","uid":21010,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f78abc950b37961a261041b0665507ad1a608afa","tid":2304803,"uid":21010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:27:04.000Z","msg":"香港教育工作者聯會（英語：Hong Kong Federation of Education Workers），簡稱教聯會或教聯，1975年4月成立的香港教職工組織，成員包括各級教育機構的校監、校長、教師和職工等，其政治立場為「愛國愛港」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=e14ac68e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【教聯會呼籲政府盡快宣布全港學校暫停面授課堂】<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情再出現反彈，連日來確診個案急升，社區出現愈來愈多源頭不明個案，當中部分涉及師生或其親友確診，情況相當嚴峻。面對流感及疫情的雙重夾擊，政府早前已先後宣布全港幼稚園及小一至小三暫停面授課堂。第四波疫情來勢洶洶，本會促請教育局必須以師生健康為首要考慮，盡快宣布全港學校暫停面授課堂，以防止校園大規模爆發疫情。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，不少小學現正安排小六生應考呈分試，而中學則為中五及中六生進行考試。為免影響進度，教聯會呼籲當局容許學校在做好防疫措施的情況下，彈性安排相關考試。<br />\n<br />\n本會亦呼籲政府加強推動有效的防疫措施，當中包括盡快推出大規模社區檢測，以及早截斷傳播鏈，讓社會早日回復正常生活，教學工作早日恢復常態。<br />\n<br />\n#教聯會 #hkfew #學校 #暫停面授課堂 #社區檢測 #齊心抗疫 #教師 #學生"},{"pid":"f2afa579c56668c008f24da59a5fe0df8ad81679","tid":2304803,"uid":204539,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:31:56.000Z","msg":"依家無選舉 唔駛玩成功爭取喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd171751ce2b5ef2160f31b8c3d9be601aab841b","tid":2304803,"uid":21010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"鋪定路下年啦 不嬲都憎教協 仲唔食住個勢咩"},{"pid":"4ce19e28a730be3ab5840b8d41af9f4161cf8093","tid":2304803,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:41:17.000Z","msg":"4號支共憲法日，當日下午宣佈停課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c208981f32e72cc9d9c9959d7289ab3c91e957f","tid":2304803,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd171751ce2b5ef2160f31b8c3d9be601aab841b","tid":2304803,"uid":21010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"鋪定路下年啦 不嬲都憎教協 仲唔食住個勢咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教聯 有冇代購美心🈷️餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/20882998_1581878741887062_1001897916390407372_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=PmaUM4VcoQIAX_AmzT5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=8fef07c7496dc777eab99c212909b9b0&amp;oe=5FE94078\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F20882998_1581878741887062_1001897916390407372_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DPmaUM4VcoQIAX_AmzT5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D8fef07c7496dc777eab99c212909b9b0%26oe%3D5FE94078&h=31ad7bdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e9936d7e7a421f53b014ef3a17314ab1bb6543c","tid":2304803,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c208981f32e72cc9d9c9959d7289ab3c91e957f","tid":2304803,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd171751ce2b5ef2160f31b8c3d9be601aab841b","tid":2304803,"uid":21010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"鋪定路下年啦 不嬲都憎教協 仲唔食住個勢咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教聯 有冇代購美心🈷️餅<img src=\"/assets/